ComicInfo.Title: They Walk Like Gods!
ComicInfo.Summary: They Walk Like Gods!: Thor and his allies continue to battle Ego-Prime. Meanwhile, Heimdall gathers together three mortals who are destined to become The Young Gods. Ego-Prime dissolves into nothingness as he tries to destroy Earth and Odin reveals that this turn of events was part of his master plan. Thor, unimpressed, berates his father.
